---
title: Lemony Cheese Tortelloni with Bacon, Peas, and Zucchini
description: Here’s some cheesy, creamy pasta-night bliss for you: these tender tortelloni are coated in a rich combination of sour cream, butter, and lemon. It’s the sort of sauce that sticks to your spoon, encouraging you to lick off every drop of deliciousness. To round things out, we’re also tossing in juicy broiled zucchini slices and crisp pancetta (those are bacon bits with Italian-style flair).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d517d66aa31b0000f29d202-6d87d13d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/lemony-cheese-tortelloni-5d517d66aa31b0000f29d202-bc41c09d.pdf
